flowchart LR
    E[Enrollment: name, phone, answers] --> SV[Derive style-v1 vector]
    SV --> DB[(SQLite profile)]
    E --> V[AES-256-GCM phone vault]
    R[Return: different answers] --> CV[Derive candidate vector]
    DB --> DR[Deterministic ranking]
    CV --> DR
    DR --> G[GPT-5.6 Sol compares two vectors]
    G --> S{Combined score >= 0.72?}
    S -- No --> N[Generic no match]
    S -- Yes --> C[Reveal name + masked phone]
    V --> O[Simulated OTP delivery]
    C --> O
    O --> H[Verify HMAC digest]
    H --> X[Verified enrolled device]

    SV -. raw answers not stored .-> DB
    G -. no name, phone, raw answers, or OTP .-> G
